reviews.reviewText: I usually use zagg privacy screen protectors and they have been out of stock and needed a new one after dropping a screwdriver on my phone. I have seen these advertised on socials and I have been super impressed and the price is really good. Will be my go to from now on.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Didn’t work, cracked immediately
reviews.reviewText: The first one I tried to apply didn’t come out of the packing correctly and so it didn’t agree at all and I had to toss it because it wasn’t sticking properly after manually removing the film covers. Second one went on just fine so I think the first one was defective, however the screen cracked within 2 days. I have had cheaper screen protectors I have dropped on asphalt from a high distance that didn’t crack at all. My daughter bumped my phone onto my carpeted floor from the couch so we’re talking maybe 2 feet drop and instantly cracked. I am extremely disappointed with this product and will have to order new set already because of the poor quality of this product. Save your money!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Easy, but more work than advertised
reviews.reviewText: I love the screen protector. The two things I would mention however is that in the video on Tik Tok, it’s shown that you can place anytime and will remove all dust/debris. It’s not the case. You do have to clean your phone with the wipe it offers to make sure all smudges and debris are fully gone. On my first one which was the clear(I got it by accident), it left some tiny debris on the bottom of the protector. The second time I ordered one which is the privacy protector, I cleaned it as perfect as I could and even used a computer duster canister to make sure it was clean. The installation came out perfect and fast. The second thing I’d say sucks is that it does smudges even after having it place, not too bad but they make it seem like it will never smudge. I’m still happy with it for the the price it was which was $27.
